{"tid":2398241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"實測中國口罩過濾率僅16.5％，無法阻擋病毒","createTime":"2021-02-07T06:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T10:37:45.000Z","uid":337052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cb42fbe1b7a713d5e975ae64e41c0a0f8d81b3ad","tid":2398241,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"中國實測「網紅口罩」過濾率僅16.5％ 網驚︰瞬間沒安全感<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/07/phpRL6aD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F07%2FphpRL6aD2.jpg&h=e1689263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國國家紡織製品質量監督檢驗中心針對網路上相當熱賣的「網紅口罩」進行測試。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/07 14:12<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕網路假貨多，口罩別亂買！近來，<span class=\"red\">中國國家紡織製品質量監督檢驗中心針對網路上相當熱賣的「網紅口罩」進行測試，結果顯示該口罩的過濾效率僅有16.5%</span>，中國網友看了紛紛驚心表示，「我開始害怕」、「我買口罩的時候都會剪開一個看看裡面有沒有熔噴布」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，現在許多口罩都號稱具備抗菌、防霾、安全防護等功效，甚至還有蒸汽發熱口罩等功能，在網路上相當熱賣，也引起相關機構的注意，中國國家紡織製品質量監督檢驗中心就對某款爆紅的「網紅口罩」進行測試，<span class=\"red\">沒想到竟顯示該口罩的過濾效率僅有16.5%，等同有超過80%的氣溶膠顆粒能毫無阻攔的通過口罩本身。</span><br />\n<br />\n對此，中國網友紛紛傻眼表示，「我開始害怕」、「瞬間沒有了安全感」、「我立馬跑去車上看我買的醫用外科口罩合不合格」、「去年一開始我買口罩的時候都會剪開一個看看裡面有沒有熔噴布」、「還是藥店的比較安全」，還有人指出，「這條新聞最應該給日本人看了，那邊一堆戴這口罩的也沒人提醒」，不過卻有人直言，「現在不少事情都涉及政治，因政治而亂來，正如我們能看到國外的不好，看不到國內的不好一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/07/phpHa4Jjh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F07%2FphpHa4Jjh.jpg&h=88aa7f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果顯示該口罩的過濾效率僅有16.5%。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/07/phpdqUufG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F07%2FphpdqUufG.jpg&h=63b67301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專家表示，這款口罩並不符合相關規範。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3434971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3434971&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=b1e9d96f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3434971&h=e3e0c6f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3434971</a>"},{"pid":"e12b6481f31c7796bbf7616c6291d5d00d10b53e","tid":2398241,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">疫情期 美截獲數百萬中國製假口罩和測試盒</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/02/Masks1-600x400.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FMasks1-600x400.jpeg&h=1aed2f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為辛辛那提海關查獲的來自中國的假冒外科口罩。（美國海關和邊境保護局官網）<br />\n更新 2021-02-06 5:11 AM"},{"pid":"ff3cb4019740694b7d12b92177b2075ad3628296","tid":2398241,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"中國國家紡織製品質量監督檢驗中心針對網路上相當熱賣的「網紅口罩」進行測試，結果顯示該口罩的過濾效率僅有16.5%"},{"pid":"535411614b32029c296c3edbaaf0977a7af36aa6","tid":2398241,"uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"我唔信測試結果"},{"pid":"5a0364bab72cb2751033386a68ee9c84be73681d","tid":2398241,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"535411614b32029c296c3edbaaf0977a7af36aa6","tid":2398241,"uid":308595,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"我唔信測試結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得入錢實肥佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab367fd585465d120fec0bf88cfde8b515b3cc32","tid":2398241,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"「去年一開始我買口罩的時候都會剪開一個看看裡面有